A great place where adults can sit on the outdoor terrace, watching the kids run around in the spacious open area.  Cyber port hosts many weekend activities making this a friendly restaurant for family.  Food is average; service could be on the slow end.
Terrible service .......45 min to even get food!

Cooked foods are cold. Ribs are totally not tender enough. Melons are tasteless. They do have crab legs and oysters. But they don't refill their food often enough, and the crab legs get emptied pretty quickly. Service is great tho, just not the food.

reviews.text: Pleasantly surprised. Great value. Very good staff. Clean room with nice view and good food. Very good value for Hong Kong.
Great room with a great view. Very good service. Perfect when having to do business in cyberport.

if you like the buzzing of the city, but a nice quiet place to relax in the evening,  this is a great choice. 

The hotel is clean and spacious , with nice clean decor. Staffs at reception and concierge are friendly and helpful.

Hotel free shuttle departs almost every hour to Hong Kong Station (Central) takes only 15 mins, so we are never far from the buzzing city. 

The arcade next door has a nice supermarket, McDonald , food court & bus terminal, and it's connected to the hotel by bridges & escalator. 

Instead of the old fashion paper tag at the door knob, you can switch on the "do not disturb" -red light   or " make room" - green light in the room, so the staffs can serve you when you are available. 

This is a pleasant surprise for our visit.
This is a great hotel! maybe one of my favorites in Hong Kong, but its too far from everything so its kinda impossible to stay here unless you are local.

Quiet hotel with nice view of the ocean and Lamma Island. Good sized rooms with a free standing bath.  Friendly staff and a good selection of food at the breakfast buffet. Outdoor pool area and link to Cyberport restaurants, cinema and waterfront park. Shuttle bus to Central Station.  Bonvoy members get additional food discounts.

reviews.text: Pleasantly surprised. Great value. Very good staff. Clean room with nice view and good food. Very good value for Hong Kong.

여행자에게 추천하기 어려운 곳입니다.  개인적인 별점은 2.5. 셔틀버스가 홍콩역까지 오가지만 호텔에서 나가는 시간이 9시가 아니면 11시로 중간 시간이 없고 홍콩역에서 들어가는 시간도 저녁7시30분을 놓치면 9시30분을 타야 합니다. 
20분 넘게 가야하는 거리라서 여행을 하면서 급하게 호텔로 들어간다거나 시내의 야경 혹은 저녁 코스는 불편함이 있습니다. 
호텔의 컨디션은 3월초에 비가 몇일간 내리는 중에도 에어컨이 돌아가기 때문에 방의 에어컨을 끄고 있어도 키를 뽑고 나가면 자동으로 에어컨인지 환기시스템인지 돌아가서 춥습니다. 
추운 부분도 있지만.  지낸 방과 다른 방 2개의 룸을 잡아서 지냈는데 모두  곰팡이 냄새가 많이 나고 침구나 방 전체가 눅눅한 느낌이라 힘들었습니다. 
여러곳을 여행하면서 가장 안좋은 느낌의 컨디션을 가진 룸이었습니다. 
다른 룸은 모르겠지만.. 

직원들은 정말 친절합니다.  대응도 빠르고 이 별점은 모두 직원들에게 주는 점수입니다. 
호텔의 특성상 시내와 떨어져 있고 비지니스 쪽에 가까운 위치 탓인지 모르겠지만.. 여행이라면 시내쪽을 추천합니다.
